properties.areaDesc: Los Angeles County Coast including Downtown Los Angeles
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 17 at 4:43AM PST until February 17 at 8:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Visibility one quarter mile or less in dense fog.

* WHERE...Los Angeles County Coast including Downtown Los
Angeles.

* WHEN...Until 8 AM PST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Very low visibility will create dangerous driving
conditions.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...1/4 mile visibility at both Los Angeles
Airport (LAX) and Long Beach Airport (LGB) were being reported. Fog
should lift before 8:00 AM.
properties.instruction:
If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of
distance ahead of you.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 AM PST THIS MORNING
